title: S12 Ep233: Shake The Devil When He Misbehaves
itunes:title: Shake The Devil When He Misbehaves
description:
Today we Shake the Devil When He Misbehaves on BEYOND the DARKNESS with guest Bill Bean.

Bill Bean has led a life filled with violent and frightening paranormal experiences and has turned his life from misery and fear to strength as he delivers people from evil forces around the world. Today he shares his most recent possession and some insights into the beasts he encounters including Bigfoot and Aliens.
